A '''joyhopper''' system allowed a [[Landspeeder/Legends|landspeeder]] to ride at a noticeably higher altitude for a short period of time. One such system was installed in the ''[[White Witch]]'' by [[Thall Joben/Legends|Thall Joben]] and [[Jord Dusat]].

